{"tid":1580116,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"為抗爭小朋友心痛","createTime":"2019-09-19T02:04:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-19T02:05:54.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8866bda3956a39e0242da22ee84bdffd287f0b01","tid":1580116,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T02:04:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20190919/20770738\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190919%2F20770738&d=gqDWnnaI%2FM4dwC7GJUFj5U63eTsi4ka8iUmrXsVTuNg%3D&h=b2268c8c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190919%2F20770738&h=9dc78eb5\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20190919/20770738</a><br />\n<br />\n為抗爭小朋友心痛<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190919/large/1568810193_e929.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190919%2Flarge%2F1568810193_e929.jpg&h=0ef42417&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n吳日言回想睇新聞見到年輕示威者被打至重傷，淚盈於睫。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n眼見現時香港局勢，不少家長已為仔女安排後路，吳日言的囡囡Bea雖然只得十個月大，萬一將來局勢有變，會送她去英國讀書。是否對香港教育制度無信心？吳日言的老公Barry坦言一直都冇，相反吳日言認為香港也有好學校，想囡囡在港讀書學中文，二人都睇中銅鑼灣的聖保祿學校。該校學生曾組人鏈表達訴求，吳日言大讚：「好勇敢，畀着我可能會諗做呢啲會唔會好辳？會唔會俾人排擠？但佢哋為自己嘅地方做嘢，有自己思想，覺得啱就行出嚟。」<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：【曾簽Juno】離開後發展更好<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190919/large/1568810192_cb37.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190919%2Flarge%2F1568810192_cb37.jpg&h=78d24c1f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n雖然囡囡只有十個月大，但吳日言坦言要為她未來作好安排。互聯網圖片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190919/large/1568810192_ab1e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190919%2Flarge%2F1568810192_ab1e.jpg&h=194b29e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n聖保祿學校學生早前組成人鏈表達訴求，吳日言大讚勇敢。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n若囡囡長大要參與示威，會否反對？吳日言謂：「我有代入去睇新聞，如果我嘅小朋友行出嚟，我上前線都冇仔女上前線咁傷心。如果個女喺最前線，唔好話受唔受傷，就算每日去抗爭，我可以為佢做啲乜？𠵱家嘅小朋友就係為我嘅下一代去爭取，所以睇到好心痛。」更越說越激動，熱淚盈眶。 <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n食店生意急挫不氣餒 吳日言逆市擴充「唔好俾難關嚇親」<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n【曾簽Juno】離開後發展更好"},{"pid":"a6b6fb15c20478cfb34c98ba6733fa3b3276b900","tid":1580116,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T02:05:54.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">[公海 文宣 行動整合] 9.29全球抗赤納粹集會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1579667\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1579667</a><br />\n全世界一齊對準ChiNazi極權！</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BZiskWr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBZiskWr.png&h=b85bf973&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">9.29 Global AntiChiNazi 文宣、資訊、行動整合Channel</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/AntiChinazi929\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FAntiChinazi929&d=gqDWnnaI%2FM4dwC7GJUFj5U63eTsi4ka8iUmrXsVTuNg%3D&h=30d6a2f8\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/AntiChinazi929</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>9.29 Global AntiChiNazi 公海</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/NfHvOU5TXSG9DxQIRNkxLQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FNfHvOU5TXSG9DxQIRNkxLQ&d=gqDWnnaI%2FM4dwC7GJUFj5U63eTsi4ka8iUmrXsVTuNg%3D&h=0502ef9e\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/NfHvOU5TXSG9DxQIRNkxLQ</a>"}]}